headline: Greif Reports Fiscal Third Quarter 2025 Results
summary: DELAWARE, Ohio, Aug. 27, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Greif, Inc. (NYSE: GEF, GEF.B), a global leader in industrial packaging products and services, today announced fiscal third quarter 2025 results. headline: Packaging Corporation Stock Outlook: Is Wall Street Bullish or Bearish?
summary: Despite Packaging Corporation's underperformance relative to the SPX over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a moderately optimistic outlook about the stock’s prospects.

headline: PCA launches carbon capture and storage study following ‘promising’ trial
summary: A pilot that Packaging Corporation of America began last year ended this summer. Now, the company works toward building a full-scale facility by 2028 and expanding the technology to other sites.
